title: The Big Suey: Enough Of Aaron Judge, Enough Of Roger Maris Jr.
description:
As Aaron Judge continues to chase HR No. 62 of the season, he and Roger Maris Jr. continue to ruin our football weekends. Then, is this an “actually, everyone is bad” year in College Football? Plus, Tony wants credit for his takes and we debate whether London is ready for their own NFL team.
